s">Well known examples of games</h2><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span cl=
ass=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/=
w/index.php?title=3DGame_theory&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D36" title=
=3D"Edit section: Well known examples of games"><span>edit</span></a><span =
class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
