<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Bertrand_Competition">Bertr=
and Competition</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editse=
ction-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?titl=
e=3DGame_theory&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D42" title=3D"Edit section: =
